org.itsnat.comp.table
Interface ItsNatTableCellUI

All Superinterfaces:
ItsNatUserData
public interface ItsNatTableCellUI
extends ItsNatUserData

Contains visual information of a table cell element.

This interface is the "componentized" version of a master TableCellElementInfo and follows a similar philosophy.

Author:
Jose Maria Arranz Santamaria
See Also:
